 News reaching us has it that a bizarre scene has played out at Ondo State House of Assembly as a live snake dropped from the roof of the chamber. Our correspondent learnt that pandemonium ensured as the lawmakers instantly fled for safety abandoning their seats to avoid being bitten by the rampaging reptile. No one could immediately ascertain whether the unwanted guest was conjured or merely chasing some rodents before accidentally landing on the floor of the House.  